{"tid":440921,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實可以搵到個共同興趣嘅男/女朋友真係好難得","createTime":"2017-10-19T08:17:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T18:35:42.000Z","uid":31209,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0bccc92b76695d91990691e0a62b4272aebb1d95","tid":440921,"uid":31209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"我意思唔係指平時一齊打下機/追星/睇動漫就算<br />\n而係不論有冇對方存在，自己都有嗰個興趣同相應嘅習慣<br />\n當兩個人共享嗰個興趣嘅時刻，係多好多重歡樂同甜蜜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見身邊有啲情侶都可能會一齊做相同興趣嘅事<br />\n但佢地最多都係唔抗拒互相陪大家做嗰樣興趣，而唔係兩個同時間都一樣咁熱愛個興趣<br />\n<br />\n搵到個肯陪自己嘅人固然甜蜜開心，而家媒體都經常吹捧「識搵一定搵個會陪你xxx嘅男/女朋友」<br />\n但我更enjoy可以搵到個另一半係同自己共享、一齊投入落個興趣到，係雙方都好有心機為自己而努力再同另一半enjoy個興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a52436005964fb656d1cf0cf7c3691c6aa1f15a","tid":440921,"uid":135986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:19:00.000Z","msg":"冇女"},{"pid":"17488ecb0550affec1ceda29d93859f0b3bf1aed","tid":440921,"uid":154436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:21:46.000Z","msg":"所有正常男人都有一個相同的興趣, 就睇女朋友有沒有姐。"},{"pid":"6668c9fe96f4b60bce93764c96d0be52cdf4e83f","tid":440921,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我意思唔係指平時一齊打下機/追星/睇動漫就算<br />\n而係不論有冇對方存在，自己都有嗰個興趣同相應嘅習慣<br />\n當兩個人共享嗰個興趣嘅時刻，係多好多重歡樂同甜蜜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見身邊有啲情侶都可能會一齊做相同興趣嘅事<br />\n但佢地最多都係唔抗拒互相陪大家做嗰樣興趣，而唔係兩個同時間都一樣咁熱愛個興趣<br />\n<br />\n搵到個肯陪自己嘅人固然甜蜜開心，而家媒體都經常吹捧「識搵一定搵個會陪你xxx嘅男/女朋友」<br />\n但我更enjoy可以搵到個另一半係同自己共享、一齊投入落個興趣到，係雙方都好有心機為自己而努力再同另一半enjoy個興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n女朋友呢啲，發夢諗下就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：諗住獨獨過世</span></strong>"},{"pid":"11b0a5418d2143005a6770caa08324f7333b2019","tid":440921,"uid":151948,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"Exact7ly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想搵個女朋友興趣都係打機、睇片、扑野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果可以早啲識到佢就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24931e8f3ce8d92216463c217351ff3a54b869b8","tid":440921,"uid":93903,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:36:11.000Z","msg":"同啲咩都冇興趣嘅人一齊應該好辛苦，因為對方唔單止對任何興趣冇興趣，仲會覺得陪你做已經好偉大付出好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ae92cd4c802e052084784095e55daeebf68e27","tid":440921,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:06:25.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遇到一個中意嘅<br />\n同我有啲似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"232cf1c923647a5a0d6f8904cb4315272bff7899","tid":440921,"uid":31209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同啲咩都冇興趣嘅人一齊應該好辛苦，因為對方唔單止對任何興趣冇興趣，仲會覺得陪你做已經好偉大付出好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當中可能都有甜蜜嘅時候嘅<br />\n但往往好多時啲人開始自私唔想遷就太多/付出就會辛苦繼而分開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fccd3dbd7f5182d3d36dceaaceb09047d31ac5","tid":440921,"uid":31209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所有正常男人都有一個相同的興趣, 就睇女朋友有沒有姐。</blockquote><br />\n搵到嘅話會好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1225108ffc9f3ae565005a7e2dbcbd51167782d2","tid":440921,"uid":129829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd1bea0325faa3af2c384fcb3ef5cbf4033bb9a","tid":440921,"uid":24642,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T17:50:52.000Z","msg":"搵到自己熱情所在本身已經係值得高興嘅事<br />\n<br />\n仲要搵到一個同聲同氣嘅人<br />\n真係好爽<br />\n大家都明個興趣嘅迷人之處<br />\n唔使花唇舌解釋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只需要靜靜地分享興趣帶嚟嘅滿足感"},{"pid":"efa855f0f5cc21826d9007bfb970c95a6c351d73","tid":440921,"uid":92456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T01:01:53.000Z","msg":"如果學巴打咁講其實好易姐你透過自己嘅興趣去識吓人未得"},{"pid":"40f01fc8654257e836e55083fffaef47c528b86a","tid":440921,"uid":76488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T01:05:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9552367ffab6639990c2a447460502c9d290f0fe","tid":440921,"uid":153837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3892e0b83a1f157f558b721c886c903a58eb3c","tid":440921,"uid":154060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"條女唔撚鐘意我 有相同興趣咪又係係度獻世 比人話當係最好朋友 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申 有一個比人拒絕 依家好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"6518cb9b39555572fefbd110cf707dc542dc9437","tid":440921,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"自己鍾意打J<br />\n女朋友都鍾意打J?"},{"pid":"774c195c426ed4bccd443de29905fc2edd2c3aea","tid":440921,"uid":154060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條女唔撚鐘意我 有相同興趣咪又係係度獻世 比人話當係最好朋友 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有一個比人拒絕 依家好唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b2057c5a8ff470d9cbf